how did you copy the profile? from which locations? I can totally see just copying the profile folder for use on another computer not working at all.. or having this problem<br /><br />how did you deploy the copied profile to all the computers?<br /><br />was it a profile you set up, and then copied from the first computer to each of the other computers?<br /><br />and is the problem that when setting that profile to load its not working because you skipped the metro settings?<br /><br />maybe the fact that you skipped the settings is also stored in your profile, so there's a conflict when trying to skip settings again on the computer you copied the profile to<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=359">Tenzen</a> — Wed Mar 20, 2013 10:15 pm</p><hr />
